    <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cncf/artwork/master/projects/kubernetes/icon/color/kubernetes-icon-color.png" alt="Kubernetes" class="floating-icon" title="Kubernetes" />
    <img src="https://www.terraform.io/images/og-image-8b3e4f7d.png" alt="Terraform" class="floating-icon" title="Terraform" />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-container">
  <div class="card about" id="about">
    <h2>üß± About Me</h2>
    <p>I'm Dave, a DevOps engineer who builds systems like LEGO sets: modular, colorful, and indestructible. I specialize in Kubernetes, CI/CD, observability, and making ops work feel like play.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card project" id="projects">
    <h2>üåç Earthquake Monitor</h2>
