    <p><a href="https://earthquakes.daveops.pro" target="_blank">üåê Visit earthquakes.daveops.pro</a></p>
  </div>
  <div class="card links" id="links">
    <h2>üîó Useful Links</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/dhiemer" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
